    <title>VeraCrypt</title>
    <authors>Mounir IDRASSI</authors>
    <owners>dtgm</owners>
    <summary>Open source disk encryption with strong security for the Paranoid </summary>
    <description>
VeraCrypt is based on the abandoned software program "TrueCrypt."  VeraCrypt adds enhanced security to the algorithms used for system and partitions encryption making it less vulnerable to brute-force attacks at the cost of slightly longer time to mount the encrypted data.

VeraCrypt storage format is INCOMPATIBLE with TrueCrypt storage format.
    </description>
